lines.text: I know who you are and what league you played in... you were Frankie Nemo's girl weren't you?

[Sarcastically]
Yass, yass... that all you have to say? Where's the cute story? Didn't he hold a mortgage on the old plantation... Wasn't he threatening the virtue of your little sister... That kind of routine? I go for cute stories.
When you think enough a lot of truths come home and stay with you.
make em beat it outta ya, eh?
